<fig id="Fig4"><label>Fig. 4</label><caption><p>KIRC expressed gene networks estimated by GGM via XMRF(…,method=~GGM~) for mRNA expression data</p></caption><graphic xlink:href="12918_2016_313_Fig4_HTML" id="MO6"/></fig></p></list-item></list></p>
